title: Rose City Band - Full Performance (Live on KEXP)
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Rose City Band performing live in the KEXP studio. Recorded May 5, 2023.

Songs:
Empty Bottles
Ramblin’ With The Day
Rabbit
Mariposa

Ripley Johnson - Guitar / Vocals
Barry Walker - Pedal Steel
Paul Hasenberg - Keyboards
Dewey Mahood - Bass
Dustin Dybvig - Drums

Host: Eva Walker
Audio Engineers: Julian Martlew & Jon Roberts
Audio Mastering: Matt Ogaz
Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Alaia D’Alessandro & Scott Holpainen
Editor: Jim Beckmann
